<li><a href="https://packages.debian.org/unstable/doc/lg-issue109">lg-issue109</a>
    -- Número 109 de la gaceta de Linux.
<li><a href="https://packages.debian.org/unstable/doc/lg-issue110">lg-issue110</a>
